normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"嘩呢篇我都睇過，我睇完覺得好感動，完全係話俾我知受傷後嘅無助唔係屬於我嘅問題，只係社會教育冇關注過點教人包扎傷口<br />\n<br />\n目送其他文都好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好講到人生唔同經歷嘅感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52f805146554d1c5a880f4b70c08b772b40294c","tid":1013994,"uid":86277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f116985b2e27e9495a54ec8b8cc8c234cb073196","tid":1013994,"uid":69013,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T10:07:04.000Z","msg":"哲學 一場思辦之旅 <br />\n<br />\n反思外國教哲學教到咁高質 <br />\n好後悔自己無勇氣問親戚借錢去外國讀U"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"佢個lecture仲好睇過本書，Youtube有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0465eb8cc301ba565c7b757d0d6035b2af8607e","tid":1013994,"uid":142359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdae4fc1fe122bc78de9d1d768404a42d8336424","tid":1013994,"uid":155262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da3b85d265b55cd5a67eecde819bd8ca08c269ea","tid":1013994,"uid":235500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5d71fb202eb350ff7e43c795318a82ad09dd5b32","tid":1013994,"uid":155262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T18:51:01.000Z","msg":"一直覺得世界好奇怪<br />\n不過自從睇過與神對話之後覺得有啲確實嘅答案<br />\n啟發咗我好多思考<br />\n但去到而家又唔覺得係絕對正確"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T15:13:15.000Z","msg":"我都有睇與神對話，宜家睇緊與神對話2，好多野都駁唔到。但係同朋友分享之後，佢話本書只係因為符合我既思考邏輯，所以我先會信。佢本人信虛無主義，覺得人生係痛苦多過歡樂，而解決痛苦既唯一方法係自殺。<br />\n<br />\n利申：重度書J"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"駁唔到嘅主因應該係佢嘅論點大多唔係經驗所得，係先驗但又不可知嘅資訊；<br />\n<br />\n睇卡謬或者尼采啦，同樣係虛無主義但係積極樂觀架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a2430369b7a7db98f5c